### REST Client para UserController
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### ========================================
### 1. CREAR USUARIO (POST)
### ========================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "juan_perez",
    "password": "password123"
}

